{"tid":1269622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【關於黑旗】網上謠傳黑旗係代表無政府主義","createTime":"2019-06-30T15:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T16:49:41.000Z","uid":18245,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a982d5ff6ac2645c907a1854a958526485600fc0","tid":1269622,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:31:10.000Z","msg":"【關於黑旗】<br />\n<br />\n網上謠傳黑旗係代表無政府主義，又ISIS又騎劫運動又乜乜物物，小編雖然唔知ISIS同光譜上左到極致嘅無政府主義有咩不為人知嘅關係，但見吹到咁離譜實在有必要同大家科普下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3EZWFMz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3EZWFMz.jpg&h=248b932a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑旗嘅正式使用，唔係嗰個搬左店去克什米爾嘅伊斯蘭國限定，而實際上伊斯蘭國用的根本就不是正宗的黑旗。黑旗在西方國家，多用於葬禮，尤其是國葬。下圖就是黑旗的使用範例：捷克前總統Vaclav Havel於2011年去世時，捷克政府就掛出了黑旗致哀。反送中運動至今，已經有三位香港人為此付出了性命，既然認同香港人作為獨立民族，以黑旗作為烈士國葬規格致哀，則可謂名正言順。<br />\n<br />\n當然，不想出來的人自然會想出一萬個理由八千個例子告訴你「不要被騎劫」、「單野好鬼」、「對準政權」之類的廢話，但如果連為付出了生命的烈士致哀的心都沒有，我們對於這種人也沒甚麼好談的了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.alamy.com/stock-photo-two-black-flags-wave-next-to-the-czech-flag-during-the-funeral-service-58062451.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alamy.com%2Fstock-photo-two-black-flags-wave-next-to-the-czech-flag-during-the-funeral-service-58062451.html&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=a05d0f5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.alamy.com/stock-photo-two-black-flags-wave-next-to-the-czech-flag-during-the-funeral-service-58062451.html</a><br />\n<br />\n更多關於黑旗意義的詳解<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mourning\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FMourning&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=8cf96e6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mourning</a>"},{"pid":"1ac8af34be3011b6e6bd7e1c81353eacd86b187b","tid":1269622,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:32:01.000Z","msg":"source:學生動源tg channel"},{"pid":"cb1a512549e9eaa97640fd05cb465544eecc6a89","tid":1269622,"uid":4942,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_black_flags\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_black_flags&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=dbbf3902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_black_flags</a><br />\n<br />\n有一定爭議性<br />\n<br />\n公眾悼念有使用<br />\n<br />\n但好多恐怖組織都用"},{"pid":"3ee7bf8c4aec503f131a0f3e8edd9d2baa258959","tid":1269622,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"阻你少少時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見到好多post話71 係去示威遊行就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位 抗爭左成個月 聽日金紫荊廣場大好機會見到政府高官 點解仲要揀去示威遊行 你地只要行出黎企出黎就幫到啲義士 唔好個個話我唔衝 無人要你衝呀 我地要人數幫啲義士cover呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我求下你地聽日朝早出黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oa6Vbqx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foa6Vbqx.jpg&h=7af281a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLcAVSd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLcAVSd.jpg&h=67b44608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dyy8wqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdyy8wqz.jpg&h=18391795&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e89124ff2b102f899914843017d84427fce7244","tid":1269622,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:49:50.000Z","msg":"升乜嘢色旗唔同人有唔同解讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c4d35dc0be49fd8dff16e2d43ca411d3be41ad","tid":1269622,"uid":33668,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:49:41.000Z","msg":"就係驚俾有心人解讀錯 然後用支持恐怖主義堵塞歐美支持（佢哋政治正確到好得人驚）<br />\n<br />\n搏唔過喎"}]}